  <title>Union_Council</title>
  <abstract>Level 4 (Union Council) of Pakistan 

Create a country wide administrative boundary dataset based on PCO (Population Census Organisation) data.

This dataset fits to GAUL (Global Administrative Unit Layer) level 0 boundaries and holds the PCO (Population Census Organisation) administrative boundaries, level 4 This release covers KPK province completely, Sindh, Punjab and Balochistan flood affected districts only. Work is undergoing to cover the rest of the country</abstract>
